WEBVTT

00:03:57.313 --> 00:04:00.333
and he specialized in the Japanese style.

00:04:00.333 --> 00:04:02.020
So little did we know that we would spend

00:04:02.020 --> 00:04:05.455
almost an entire year painting that river,

00:04:05.455 --> 00:04:09.175
together with Geovani
and Robinho and Vitor,

00:04:09.175 --> 00:04:11.301
who lived nearby.

00:04:11.301 --> 00:04:13.371
And we even moved into the neighborhood

00:04:13.371 --> 00:04:16.734
when one of the guys that 
lived on the street, Elias,

00:04:16.734 --> 00:04:19.659
told us that we could come 
and live in his house,

00:04:19.659 --> 00:04:21.007
together with his family,

00:04:21.007 --> 00:04:22.477
which was fantastic.

00:04:22.477 --> 00:04:23.805
Unfortunately, during that time,

00:04:23.805 --> 00:04:26.086
another war broke out between the police

00:04:26.086 --> 00:04:27.861
and the drug gangs.

00:04:27.861 --> 00:04:32.609
(Video) (Gunfire)